<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٦٢٥ -<span class="c5"> وَعَنْ عُمَرَ بْنِ الْخَطَّابِ:</span> <span class="c2">«أَنَّهُ كَانَ يَقْطَعُ مِنَ الْمَفْصِلِ»</span> وَفِي إِسْنَادِ هَذَا الْحَدِيثِ مَقَالٌ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>